                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;It has been a pleasure to be a part of your 10X Health Care Team!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;I&amp;#39;d like to introduce you to my colleague, Kristin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Kristin is your Wellness Concierge. Her responsibility is to handhold you on your journey to optimal health! Krisitn will be your point of contact moving forward to ensure we set you up for success along the way!&amp;nbsp;Here&amp;#39;s a little more about your Concierge:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Kristin Cornett is a Functional Nutritional Therapy Practitioner with nearly a decade of experience in the health and wellness field. She has advanced training in functional lab testing and interpretation and extensive experience working with clients to improve gut health, metabolic health, hormone balance, fertility, immune system challenges, nutritional deficiencies, and lifestyle concerns. She is also completing a training program focused on nervous system regulation and trauma resolution that helps clients heal from disease-promoting chronic stress&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Kristin&amp;nbsp;came to health and wellness work after experiencing a series of personal health challenges that were not being adequately addressed by the traditional medical approach. Finding profound healing through nutrition and integrative medicine is what sparked her passion to help others discover their unique path to restored health.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Kristin, {{{Recipient.FirstName}}} shared some of the top wellness goals below:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;INSERT GOALS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;INSERT GOALS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;INSERT GOALS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}}, Kristin is fully prepared to provide you with the support you need to 10X your health through monthly check ins, answering questions, and keeping you on track on with your protocol!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Your first meeting with Kristin will be on &lt;strong&gt;[Date &amp;amp; Time]&lt;/strong&gt;. Keep an eye out for a calendar invite and reminders coming your way! Kristin will connect with you to go over your next steps: completing an inventory check, walking you through your protocol, and ensuring you feel fully confident with your medications when they arrive.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Heads up&lt;/b&gt;: If anything&amp;nbsp;is lost, missing, or damaged, please let us know within 24 hours and send a quick photo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In the meantime, if you have any questions or need to reschedule your call with Kristin, please don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reply to this email or click on the scheduling link.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://&quot;&gt;https://calendly.com/kcornett-10xhealthsystem/precision-wellness-protocol-welcome-inventory-check&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;You can contact Kristin directly via email at&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;kcornett@10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In Health,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Your 10X Care Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
